   ``Get lost,'' Nicholas says.
</P>
<P>
   Kids these days. No respect. (I'm nearing retirement age by this
time. I'm supposed to spout off about youngsters.)
</P>
<P>
   I've been waiting for you to become a grown-up, Nicholas is
told. There are things no one could ask you back in 2000, when you
were only 2.
</P>
<P>
   ``Like what?''
