</P>
<P>
   Don't you hate her for that?
</P>
<P>
   ``No.''
</P>
<P>
   Why not? I can't imagine a worse thing a parent could say about
her child.
</P>
<P>
   ``Back in 2000,'' Nicholas says, ``did anyone claim my mother
had abandoned me?''
</P>
<P>
   No.
</P>
<P>
   ``Was she accused of physically abusing me?''
</P>
<P>
   No.
</P>
<P>
   ``Did she fail to give me clothes or food, or to put a roof over
my head?''
</P>
<P>
   No.
</P>
