<HEADLINE>
EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   Good morning. The New York Times News Service has reopened for
the day.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Questions or reruns: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   The day supervisor is Gary McCardell.
