</P>
<P>
   PATENTS (Undated) _ The weekly patents column: a new
``omnidirectional'' top made of small acrylic spheres spins even
though it has no pointed edge; a playhouse that resembles a
miniature church, with steeple, stained glass windows, pews and a
working sound system that plays hymns, wedding music and sermons;
and a vacuum cleaner attachment that filters tiny toys like Barbie
accessories and Lego pieces. By Teresa Riordan.
