<P>
   OLYMPICS
</P>
<P>
   OLY-FOXHALL _Wrap-up on the inaugural Foxhall cup, winners and
losers and an assessment of the success of the event, which will be
Atlanta's annual prestigious equine competition. (Teegardin,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
<P>
   GLF_ IRWIN _ Feature on Hale Irwin, who had dominated the Senior
PGA Tour the past 4 years, but is finding the going tougher with
the emergence of Bruce Fleisher, the newcomers like Tom Watson, Tom
Kite and Lanny Wadkins, and the fine play of Marietta's Larry
Nelson. (Sheeley, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
