   BC-CENSUS-RETURNS-NYT OLY-SOCCER (moved on Wednesday, May 3)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, May 3
about the rate at which Americans are returning census forms
misstated the latest date for which detailed state-by-state
response figures were available. It was April 24, not April 4.
