ice cream, on 137th street and Amsterdam Avenue in uptown
Manhattan, from Vincent Garcia an ice cream truck driver who has
been serving the neighborhood for more than 27 years. As warmer
temperatures finally hit New York, many people quickly sought
relief from the first signs of summer. (Vincent Laforet/The New
York Times)
</P>
<P>
