<HEADLINE>
VICTIM'S WIFE HAD BOUGHT POWER SAW 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 BY CHRISTINA LEONARD AND BETH DEFALCO  
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
